<div class="section">
  <h1>Exclusive Licensed 5G Spectrum Access in the USA</h1>
  <p>
    This guide details how US enterprises can obtain exclusive access to licensed 5G spectrum <b>without participating in auctions</b>. Options include spectrum assignment (purchase/transfer), leasing, and sub-licensing via spectrum managers. All recommended steps, available frequencies, and direct contacts are included.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="section">
